'''Lot ZX1449F''' was a batch of [[Bacta/Legends|bacta]] produced by the [[Xucphra Corporation]]. [[Ashern]] rebels sabotaged the bacta in ZX1449F, which was sent to [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] and infected two million people. All patients treated with this lot became severely allergic to bacta, and approximately two percent contracted [[blastonecrosis]].

After discovering this, [[Ysanne Isard]] had the lot eliminated by flooding it onto the black market.

